title: Tech trio set to compete at USATF Golden Games - VT hokiesports.com
content: Tech trio set to compete at USATF Golden Games  VT hokiesports.com
description: Tech track & field has added a new meet to its 2022 outdoor schedule, as pole vaulters Rachel Baxter, Julia Fixsen, and volunteer assistant coach Bridget Williams are headed to Walnut, Calif. this weekend to compete in the USATF Golden Games at the Mt. SAC Relays
